{"tid":123392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過一見鍾情","createTime":"2017-02-16T23:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T00:42:59.000Z","uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fffcd97ebc14831ad9926e23dc42ac1aa34573cb","tid":123392,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T23:53:22.000Z","msg":"我好似一見鍾情左一個女仔<br />\n但佢有個好好既男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019d67a6ddfa16953ccaa691cc50c648160ab660","tid":123392,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T23:54:23.000Z","msg":"唔好諗 快啲忘記佢 唔會有結果㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac714513cce0cb5ee1d44e5a6ad87b91de142b3","tid":123392,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好諗 快啲忘記佢 唔會有結果㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我好少可會見到佢 亦都冇乜機會傾計<br />\n仲要有一段長時間冇見過 但係都會成日諗起佢<br />\n依家一有機會見到佢就會想借啲咦同佢相處下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都知佢有男朋友我唔應該搞佢<br />\n但其實比我望下佢個樣 同佢傾兩句就已經好開心好舒服"},{"pid":"6efe596513ab19718c250ca8a806cd4f198e7dc6","tid":123392,"uid":30708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:02:33.000Z","msg":"一見鐘情 有試過，<br />\n只有你鐘意人，人地只會當你狗公<br />\n唔好試，快d忘記佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93c182c7f5d2d50539a669b94f0f746c2b2a5b5","tid":123392,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:03:24.000Z","msg":"試下啦撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母咪搞鳩人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b128630013e726ceae695ff95045440e1f90befb","tid":123392,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一見鐘情 有試過，<br />\n只有你鐘意人，人地只會當你狗公<br />\n唔好試，快d忘記佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲忘記佢 間唔中都會見到佢<br />\n仲會有機會一齊共事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢都肯同我玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e30c37032761f7659d5c899e85d5f63f321876e","tid":123392,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下啦撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母咪搞鳩人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試乜鳩姐<br />\n我其實都冇諗住溝走佢<br />\n佢地好幸福 我都唔想破壞佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8871dcfb8b503b72b768b5ec1ca14ef4eabe855b","tid":123392,"uid":76253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:07:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好似一見鍾情左一個女仔<br />\n但佢有個好好既男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一乜撚野鐘情<br />\n米又見人靚女扯撚哂旗"},{"pid":"587af60fac8e89ac2d45809ad50acbb773b6e033","tid":123392,"uid":39902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:09:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd54459eaf347a0cb70ee29cb4cdafc3f66ad4fb","tid":123392,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我好似一見鍾情左一個女仔<br />\n但佢有個好好既男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一乜撚野鐘情<br />\n米又見人靚女扯撚哂旗</blockquote><br />\n佢唔係好靚女架咋<br />\n我好清楚唔係因為佢靚<br />\n因為我見到靚女就唔係呢種感覺<br />\n至少我會j靚女但唔會j佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a1cf5322aff26acff76790fbd0978b7af2feda","tid":123392,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T00:12:17.000Z"